        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 11. Sahastata nigra (Simon, 1897), endogyne, ventral.A Paralectotype from Muscat, Oman (MNHN AR 5476); B–C Jebel Shams mountains, Oman (MACN-Ar 38368); D–F Quriyat, Oman (MACN-Ar 39467); F Anterior margin of interpulmonary fold. Abbreviations: GPS—glandular portion of spermathecae; IF—interpulmonary fold; MPS—membranous portion of spermathecae." ;
